Package: transform
Title: Lightweight and robust functions for common variable transformations in R
Version: 0.2.3
Authors@R: person("Derek", "Damron", email = "damrondm@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: transform provides lightweight and robust functions for common variable transformations.
    Transformations supported include trimming and rescaling for numeric variables, regrouping
    for categorical variables, and imputing for either variable type.
Depends: R (>= 3.2.0)
Suggests:
    devtools,
    testthat
License: file LICENSE
LazyData: true
LinkingTo: Rcpp
Imports: Rcpp
